Class FlightTest

java.lang.Object
bcu.cmp5332.bookingsystem.test.FlightTest
public class FlightTest extends Object
Comprehensive test class for Flight model. Tests all flight functionality including constructors, getters, setters, passenger management, pricing, and detail formatting.
